cs.RO, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG 

This paper addresses the problem of natural language understanding for domestic service robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper proposes a multimodal target-source classifier model that uses linguistic and visual features to classify regions in the scene as potential targets or sources. This involves natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO, followed by cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.LG.
